      "category": "NEWS",
      "date": "Apr 23, 2026",
      "html": "<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0b2149 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b0b2149\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>“Truly love yourself as you are. Confidence and authenticity are everything! People connect with real energy” &#8211;<a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bendydasha_/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Dasha</a></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dc71a51 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"dc71a51\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0fd695f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0fd695f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-025525a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"025525a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">How would you describe your style?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">I’m known for my aesthetic driven visual style. My work focuses on creating strong, visually engaging content that blends sensuality, creativity, and storytelling.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What does the SX / Adult / Pleasure community mean to you?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">To me, the pleasure community is about freedom, self-expression, and connection. It’s a space where people can explore identity, desire, and creativity without judgment, while being part of a supportive and open minded environment.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What has been your most memorable moment in your career so far?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">One of the most memorable parts of my career has been the journey itself growing into my identity, building confidence, and connecting with people who truly resonate with my work and energy.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7dafe95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7dafe95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What people often don’t see is the amount of work, consistency, and emotional investment that goes into building and maintaining this kind of presence!</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49f43b6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"49f43b6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5dd967d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5dd967d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"515\" height=\"760\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/8768.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1738\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/8768.webp 515w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/8768-203x300-1.webp 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 515px) 100vw, 515px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ecd8808 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ecd8808\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eff4555 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eff4555\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What is inspiring you right now?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Right now, I’m really inspired by learning how to evolve creatively and expand what I do, both visually and conceptually. It’s about pushing boundaries and exploring new ways of expression.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What inspired you to join SX Festival this year?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">I’m excited to join SX Festival and Expo because it brings together a unique mix of people, ideas, and creative energy. It feels like the right space to connect and grow.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><strong><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">What can people expect from you at SX Festival &amp; Expo?</span></strong></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">People can expect me to show up fully, bringing my energy, my aesthetic, and my presence into the space. It’s about creating an experience, not just showing up.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Choose your ticket with </span><a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://www.eventbrite.ie/e/sx-festival-sx-expo-2026-berlin-tickets-1550925051579\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DASHA15 </a><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">discount code</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a984fd3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a984fd3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</div>"
